cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CE, cs.LG

This paper deals with game theory and the study of human behavior in games. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Computer Science - Game Theory). The paper also discusses the role of artificial intelligence in modeling human behavior, which suggests the category cs.AI (Computer Science - Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses social influence, which suggests the category cs.SI (Computer Science - Social and Information Networks). The paper also discusses fairness and altruism, which suggests the category cs.CE (Computer Science - Computational Economics and Finance). Finally, the paper also discusses statistical learning, which suggests the category cs.LG (Computer Science - Machine Learning).
